                            <comment id="17877926" author="edimitrova" created="Fri, 30 Aug 2024 00:42:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Seen here - &lt;a href=&quot;https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/ekaterinadimitrova2/cassandra/2731/workflows/b987651a-5280-4dd6-9895-3298456406c8/jobs/61557/tests&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/ekaterinadimitrova2/cassandra/2731/workflows/b987651a-5280-4dd6-9895-3298456406c8/jobs/61557/tests&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17879314" author="dcapwell" created="Wed, 4 Sep 2024 17:33:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Getting ready to merge &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-19847&quot; title=&quot;Create a fuzz test that randomizes topology changes, cluster actions, and CQL operations&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-19847&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-19847&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; which makes hung jvm-dtest clusters print their stack trace (so you can see what is blocking)... here is what is blocking for me&lt;/p&gt;

